Class SearchDataView

  • java.lang.Object
    • views.SearchDataView

  • public class SearchDataView
extends java.lang.Object
    SearchDataView is the main class that holds the information for the Search and Collection Screen. This class's VBox contains the search bar, reset Button, navigation buttons, advanced search, TableView of Records, and the export PDF button. The navigation buttons of Dance, Publication, Recording, or Album determine the state's changing to "d", "p", "r", or "a" respectively.
    Author:
    lisaketcham
